Uses of Package
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.interfaces

Packages that use com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.interfaces
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model Provides the classes that the RESTful API will interact with. 
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl Provides the classes that implement model entities that the RESTful interface will interact with 
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.hbasemrlazy Provides classes that 'lazily' allow their members to persist their own membership and use Map/Reduce to determine attributes about themselves. 
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.inMemory Provides classes that support a simple in-memory implementation of the various model classes. 
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.lazy Provides classes that 'lazily' allow their members to persist their own membership. 
com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.interfaces   
com.github.seqware.queryengine.plugins Provides the interfaces that an external plugin developer would need to conform to in order for the Query Engine to install and run properly.
